data.title: House of Göholms, Ronneby Municipality Podcast
data.meta_description: Did you know that in Sweden there is a historic residence intertwined with the life of a naval hero? Göholms House, located in the county of Blekinge, is an architectural gem nestled in the parish of Listerby, belonging to the municipality of Ronneby.
